a:11:{s:7:"content";s:4142:"
  
    



<div class="border-box">
<div class="border-tl"><div class="border-tr"><div class="border-tc"></div></div></div>
<div class="border-ml"><div class="border-mr"><div class="border-mc float-break">

<div class="content-view-full">
    <div class="class-folder">

        <div class="attribute-header">
            <h2 class="section-title" style="text-transform: capitalize;">
about</h2>
        </div>

	
<div class="section-description">
	                            <div class="attribute-short">
                    
<p>Welcome to Hacker News [Delta] the social networking news website where the news is user submitted and moderated.</p><p>Start by creating a account and then voting for your favorite stories on <a href="/all" target="_self">/all</a>/<a href="/all/upcoming" target="_self">upcoming</a>, advanced users should submit news stories for others to vote.</p><p><b>Instructions</b>: <a href="/user/register" target="_self">Signup</a> or <a href="/user/login" target="_self">login</a> and then <b><i>navigate to a sub </i></b><u><a href="/c" target="_self">category</a></u> to be able to submit your own unique news story for others to vote for!</p>                </div>
                    
                    <div class="attribute-long rich-text">
                
<a name="eztoc285_1" id="eztoc285_1"></a><h2>About HND: Hacker News Delta</h2><p>Hacker News Delta is an open source website clone of <a href="https://News.YCombinator.com" target="_self">News.YCombinator.com</a> built upon hackerNewsClone (Exponential 6.x).</p><p>Everyone is free to register for an account and use the website to read, vote and submit news to the world.</p><a name="eztoc285_2" id="eztoc285_2"></a><h2>About the word &quot;Delta&quot;</h2><p>Delta means the following key things.</p>
<ul>

<li>Definition for <a href="https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/delta" target="_self">Delta from merriam-webster</a>.
<ul>

<li>&quot;the triangular or fan-shaped piece of land made by deposits of mud and sand at the mouth of a river&quot;</li>

<li>&quot;communications code word&quot;</li>

<li>&quot;the 4th letter of the Greek alphabet&quot;</li>

</ul>
</li>

</ul>
<p>For us Delta means where convergence occurs and exponential synergies emerge down stream (internet).</p>            </div>
        </div>
        

    	<div class="content-view-children float-break generic-content-list">
    	                                    

<div class="content-view-line generic-content-item">
    <div class="class-folder">

        <h3 class="generic-content-title" style="text-transform: capitalize;"><a href="/about/faq" class="link">faq</a></h3>

                    <div class="attribute-short">
                
<p>Hacker News [Delta] - FAQ covering the main questions and topics related to HND.&nbsp;</p>            </div>
                
    </div>
</div>            
                                             

<div class="content-view-line generic-content-item">
    <div class="class-folder">

        <h3 class="generic-content-title" style="text-transform: capitalize;"><a href="/about/legal" class="link">legal</a></h3>

                    <div class="attribute-short">
                
<p>Legal information regarding the use of this website.</p>            </div>
                
    </div>
</div>            
                                             

<div class="content-view-line generic-content-item">
    <div class="class-folder">

        <h3 class="generic-content-title" style="text-transform: capitalize;"><a href="/about/contact" class="link">contact</a></h3>

                    <div class="attribute-short">
                
<p>Hacker News Delta is an open website product project by 7x.</p><p>For any issue you might have, feel free to <a href="/about/contact" target="_self">contact the HNDelta Crew</a> directly.</p>            </div>
                
    </div>
</div>            
